dct_title_s: Rutgers University, New Brunswick, New Jersey campuses 1973
dct_description_sm: Verso of maps of Rutgers University, College Avenue and Douglass Campuses in New Brunswick, New Jersey. Front page features Rutgers University seal and text descriptions About Rutgers. Inside page features inset map of all New Brunswick area campuses surrounded by advertisements.
